com.sun.identity.federation.message

Class FSAssertion

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.identity.saml.assertion.AssertionBase
      • com.sun.identity.saml.assertion.Assertion
        • com.sun.identity.federation.message.FSAssertion

  • public class FSAssertion
extends Assertion
    The class FSAssertion creates and parses Liberty Assertion during the Single Sign-On process. This class extends from SAML Assertion.
